    <item>
      <title>华为 Pura 80 快登陆香港？ 官方新片「港味直出」宣传免 P 图捕捉「港味」时刻</title>
      <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/07/02/pura-80-hong-kong/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=pura-80-hong-kong</link>
      <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/07/02/pura-80-hong-kong/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
      <dc:creator>Lawton</dc:creator>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Jul 2025 12:00:34 +0000</pubDate>
      <category>手提电话</category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1314674</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;华为日前在官方微博释出一段在香港拍摄，以「个性色卡，港味直出」为主题的 &lt;a href="https://m.weibo.cn/status/5183598287915868?sourceType=weixin&amp;amp;from=10F6495060&amp;amp;wm=9006_2001&amp;amp;featurecode=newtitle&amp;amp;s_channel=4&amp;amp;s_trans=7498412102_5183598287915868&amp;amp;jumpfrom=weibocom#&amp;amp;video"&gt;Pura 80 Pro+ 宣传片&lt;/a&gt;，Pura 80 系列于香港发售似乎指日可待。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1314681" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070251340-694x401.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="401" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070251340-694x401.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070251340.jpg 746w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pura 80 系列的卖点在于强大的 AI 功能，如可以随时配合图片，文件等回答问题的智慧 AI 助手「小艺」，防窥保护屏幕，降噪通话，隔空传送功能等，甚至手机主题的互动小生物「憨憨」，在不同层面上均呈现无处不在的 AI 运用。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1314725" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/761f1940422811f0b57f-1-694x365.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="365" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/761f1940422811f0b57f-1-694x365.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/761f1940422811f0b57f-1.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1314724" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/untitleddesign202506-580x580.png" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/untitleddesign202506-580x580.png 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/untitleddesign202506.png 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/untitleddesign202506-144x144.png 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;宣傅片中所见，由艺人陈贝儿带领观众探索香港不同的颜色，大力强调手机的拍摄及调色功能，可以拍出色彩鲜艳的的相片。影片中介绍了多个香港著名的打卡点，例如中环电梯，蓝田巴士总站，彩虹村等，重点宣传「Pura 个性色卡」，而以香港为拍摄地的宣传片亦似乎意味 Pura 80 系列即将在香港发售，甚至有机会推出国际版。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1314678" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070251104-694x392.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="392" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070251104-694x392.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070251104.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1314679" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070251117-694x392.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="392" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070251117-694x392.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070251117.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;「Pura 个性色卡」是什么？&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;简单来说，色卡就是滤镜，相机有 4 款内置色卡：自然，胶片，电影和动漫。用户可在选定色卡后再自订色温，饱和度，光影三大原素，只需在莹幕下方滑动调色版，即可轻易调出理想氛围。色卡可以在拍摄前直接调整，直出相片，方便用户省略了后制照片的步骤。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1314680" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070242544-694x392.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="392" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070242544-694x392.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070242544.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1314732" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070233437-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070233437-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070233437.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1314733" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070233439-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070233439-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070233439.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;而这次港版宣传侧重介绍胶片风，影片中多处用即影即有菲林的格式突显出胶片风拍摄出色彩鲜明，「浓郁直给，港味十足」的「胶片故事」的效果。有了个性色卡的功能，要拍出怀旧港产片的味道也轻松无难度。如果你喜欢照片有怀旧风又嫌后制过程麻烦，可以期待官方消息了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1314687" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070243736-2-694x392.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="392" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070243736-2-694x392.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070243736-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1314734" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070233346-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070233346-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070233346.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1314735" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070233315-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070233315-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025070233315.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
